project_descr: As follow-up to Sudan DDR Programme, this multi sectoral programme is developed to achieve peace and stability through community security, stabilization and reintegration, in the transitional areas.

outputs.output_descr: The stabilization project aims to support stability and peace building by strengthening the resilience of communities which are at a higher risk of being drawn into conflict.
donor_name: MINISTRY  OF FOREIGN AFFAIRS & COOPERATION OF SPAIN
